{subhead}Pegasos to go on sale on Monday - Pegasos II to be available in September 2003{def}
{left}
{pp}
21.2.2003
{pp}
There are 300 to sell and a 100 that will go to MorphOS Developers and Employees.
{pp}
If interested to purchase a Pegasos mainboard or fully configured machine:{p}
1. Contact your Distributor{p}
2. Contact Phoenix{p}
3. Contact Genesi
{pp}
When these are sold there will not be another release until August/September 2003.
The next release, the Pegasos II, will have double data rates, three 1 Gb/s ethernet
channels, and Dual G4s. Genesi will not release a new version until then.
{pp}
We want everyone to understand this before they purchase the Pegasos available now.
All Betatester boards will be exchanged with the first priority.
{pp}
An upgrade credit will be offered to Pegasos I buyers. The Pegasos I will not have a
G4 upgrade.
{pp}
